</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id="Case_1:_if_i_and_j_are_in_different_blocks">Case 1: if i and j are in different blocks</h4><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Lowest_common_ancestor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Case 1: if i and j are in different blocks"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
